# Integrations

Third-party SDKs initialized in this app — analytics, error tracking, email, session replay, feature flags, etc. **Specialize this doc** to the SDKs actually present (read the entry file before writing).

## Ownership

This doc owns SDK init, key/secret handling, env branching, and load order. Per-feature usage (e.g. "how to track a button click in component X") stays close to the feature — do not duplicate call sites here.

If an SDK exposes an HTTP-style client that the app actually uses for arbitrary API calls (not just SDK-internal), prefer documenting that part in `patterns/api-integration.md` and cross-link.

