## Init order rules

{{INIT_ORDER}}

<!--
  Rationale for the order, and any "must be before X" constraints:

  - Error tracker first — so any throw during later init is captured.
  - Analytics second — so identify() can run as soon as auth resolves.
  - Session replay third — recording can start mid-session.
  - Feature flags before any feature-flag-gated code path runs (often this
    means before React hydration).

  If an SDK is init'd lazily (only on a specific page or interaction), say so
  here and link to the file.
-->

